building_description:
D1 Tower is a luxurious 80-storey residential tower located in Dubai Culture Village. Rising 280 meters above the Dubai Creek, it offers breathtaking views of the water and the Burj Khalifa. The D1 tower is a waterfront development situated adjacent to the Palazzo Versace Dubai Hotel that offers studios and one to four bedroom apartments and penthouses.

D1 Tower offers ultra-modern design with premium quality finishes, by combining Middle Eastern heritage with contemporary features such as state-of-the-art technology and facilities.

Culture Village, Dubai is a world-class destination that offers old-world elegance with a modern and sophisticated ambience. It offers a waterfront promenade with lots of open spaces, cobblestone walkways and bridges and both commercial and residential districts. Culture Village is home to the Palazzo Versace, the Iris Asmar and the D1 Tower.

What’s Offered?


	Studios
	1 Bedroom apartments
	2 Bedroom apartments
	3 Bedroom apartments
	4 Bedroom apartments
	Sub Penthouses
	Penthouses


D1 Tower at Culture Village Features


	Bosch & Miele appliances or equivalent. Appliances include microwave, dishwasher, gas cook top and range hood.
	Extraction fans in kitchen, laundry and all bathrooms
	Multi zoned air conditioning
	Front door intercom with video screen
	All services individually metered (except gas)
	Dark brown mahogany parquetry throughout the bedroom floor
	Floor to ceiling windows


D1 Tower at Culture Village Amenities


	Indoor
	Swimming pool
	Gymnasium
	Male & Female sauna, steam and change rooms
	Kids club
	Cinema
	Landscaped park surrounding the tower
	Residents lounge
	Lagoon pool
	Poolside terraces
	Reading lounge
	Retail space on ground floor

building_description:
Nestled amidst the vibrant Opera District, Il Primo offers an unparalleled living experience in Downtown Dubai. Just steps away from the iconic Dubai Opera, this luxurious development boasts spacious apartments with breathtaking views of the city's skyline.
Residents of Il Primo enjoy easy access to the city's most celebrated landmarks, including Burj Khalifa, The Dubai Mall, Souk Al Bahar, and Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid Boulevard. With its prime location and excellent connectivity to major roads and the Dubai Metro, Il Primo provides effortless access to the entire city.
Beyond its exceptional location, Il Primo offers a world of amenities and conveniences. Relax and unwind in the infinity pool overlooking Burj Khalifa, indulge in delicious dining options, or explore the nearby retail destinations. Experience the epitome of luxury living at Il Primo, where comfort, convenience, and breathtaking views come together seamlessly.

The Burj Vista is an architectural tribute to the iconic Burj Khalifa, offering uninterrupted views of the Burj Khalifa. The Burj Vista consists of two 20 and 65-storey towers located on Mohammed Bin Rashid Boulevard, offering 120 and 520 luxury apartments in one to three-bedroom layouts.
 
This highly sought-after location not only offers stunning views of Downtown Dubai, but its prime location makes it a walking distance to The Dubai Mall and Dubai's central business district as well as close to the upcoming Opera District.
 
The towers will also be directly linked to the newly opened pedestrian link that connects the Dubai Metro station with Downtown Dubai. The boulevard level of the towers will feature several high-end retail outlets and restaurants.

State-of-the-art gymnasium
Swimming pool
Children's play areas and pool
Badminton and basket ball court
Reading areas
Lush landscaped areas
Games room
Lounge
Community hall
BBQ area

Nearby Places

Located right on Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid Blvd
Minutes away from the Burj Khalifa/Dubai Mall Metro Station

building_description:
Sobha The S Tower is a 751-ft luxury residential building in Al Sufouh district, Dubai. Developed by Sobha Realty, the building will have 43 residential levels housing 4 and 5-bedroom apartments.
Location
Al Sufouh is a prime area of Dubai, located between Dubai Media City and the famous Palm Jumeirah. The area is home to a number of multinational companies, as well as the free economic zones of Dubai Internet City and Dubai Knowledge Village.
Amenities
The building will offer world-class amenities, including:

6 levels of enclosed podium parking
6 destination-controlled residential elevators
Lobby
Concierge services
Sauna
Gym
Dedicated floor with cafe, majlis, and business center

Target Audience
Sobha The S Tower is targeted at high-net-worth individuals and families who are looking for luxury living in a prime location. The building's amenities and location make it ideal for both residents and investors.
Investment Potential
Al Sufouh is a popular area for investment, with an average return on investment of 4-5%. However, given the colossal plans of the Dubai Government, the potential yield could be much higher.
Overall, Sobha The S Tower is a luxury residential development in a prime location with world-class amenities. It is targeted at high-net-worth individuals and families who are looking for the best that Dubai has to offer.

Welcome to ORLA, an epitome of luxury and sophistication, brought to life by OMNIYAT, one of Dubai's leading upscale property developers. Situated on the prestigious western crescent of Palm Jumeirah, ORLA stands as a testament to opulence and exclusivity, offering a curated collection of bespoke residences designed to redefine luxury living.
Unparalleled Elegance
ORLA features a meticulously designed 13-story building housing 93 exquisite properties, ranging from 2 to 4-bedroom apartments, simplexes, and 4-bedroom duplexes. These residences are available in various sizes, starting from 3,276 sq. ft. and reaching up to a lavish 11,064 sq. ft. The development aims to set new standards for luxury living in Dubai.
A Legacy of Luxury Management
The exquisite residences at ORLA will be expertly managed by the renowned Dorchester Collection, a prestigious boutique hotel brand with a heritage dating back to 1889. Renowned for its legacy of luxury, style, and refinement, Dorchester Collection oversees some of the world's most iconic 5-star hotels, setting the industry standard for excellence and innovation.
Unrivaled Panoramic Views
ORLA residents will enjoy breathtaking 270-degree views of the shimmering Arabian Gulf, thanks to the prime location of the building on Palm Jumeirah's crescent.
Elevated Lifestyle
ORLA's residences have been thoughtfully designed with utmost attention to detail. Depending on the layout, residences span one or two floors and feature a maid's room, a preparatory kitchen, a breakfast area, and a welcoming foyer. The select 4-bedroom duplexes offer a private swimming pool, creating a resort-like ambiance. Each residence is equipped with 2, 3, or 4 parking spaces for maximum convenience.
Chic and Spacious Interiors
The interiors of ORLA properties exude elegance with a blend of rose petal colors and soft brown wood palettes. Residents can revel in the expansive private terraces, panoramic floor-to-ceiling windows, fully-equipped branded kitchens, smart home systems, and generously sized bedrooms. Some simplexes feature ceilings ranging from 10 to 22 feet, adding a sense of spaciousness to the premium living spaces.
Exclusive Investment Opportunities
ORLA offers discerning property buyers the opportunity to own a piece of this super-elite development, with prices starting at AED 26.7 million (USD 7.3 million). For those seeking the utmost privacy and exclusivity, opulent palatial mansions are available at approximately AED 250 million (USD 68 million).
The Epitome of Luxury Living
Nestled at the apex of Palm Jumeirah's crescent, ORLA by OMNIYAT is surrounded by a wealth of luxury hotels, fine dining, and entertainment options, making it the epitome of luxury living in Dubai. Whether it's The 8 Palm, W Dubai  The Palm, or world-class restaurants and entertainment venues, everything you desire is at your doorstep.
Endless Leisure Options
ORLA residents have access to a plethora of leisure activities, including Nakheel Mall, Golden Mile Galleria, Al Ittihad Park, and the world's tallest 360-degree panoramic pool, AURA Skypool at The Palm Tower. For those seeking adventure, the Aquaventure Waterpark promises excitement and thrills, all within the captivating surroundings of Palm Jumeirah.
ORLA by OMNIYAT stands as a true masterpiece of luxury, offering a lifestyle that's second to none in the heart of Dubai's most iconic locale, Palm Jumeirah.

One Canal is a premier new residential development in Dubai, offering a collection of exclusive Penthouses, Sky Villas, and a Sky Mansion along the Dubai Water Canal. Developed by AHS Properties, this project is designed to set new standards for luxury living, featuring a range of high-end amenities and opulent residences with stunning views.
Key Features of One Canal:

Exclusive Residences: The project includes 24 Penthouses, Sky Villas, and one Sky Mansion, with options ranging from 3 to 5 bedrooms.
Spacious Living Areas: Penthouses range from 4,100 to 6,725 sq. ft., while Sky Villas range from 7,190 to 9,000 sq. ft.
Luxury Amenities: Residents enjoy round-the-clock concierge services, a dedicated concierge app, a residents' lounge, a screening room, a cigar lounge, chauffeur service, a gym, a yoga studio, a world-class spa, an indoor swimming pool, and a pool lounge.
Innovative Design: The building features private elevators that open directly into living rooms, ceiling heights from 13 to 30 feet, and a facade incorporating green pockets and wave-inspired architecture.
Strategic Location: Situated along the Dubai Water Canal, close to Safa Park, with easy access to Al Wasl Road, Sheikh Zayed Road, Downtown Dubai, and Dubai International Airport.
Flexible Payment Plan: The project offers a post-handover payment plan of 60/40, with a starting price of AED 18M for a 3-bedroom Penthouse and AED 28M for a 4-bedroom Sky Villa.

Additional Highlights:

Opulent Interiors: Each residence includes a show kitchen, back kitchen, master lounge, guest rooms, staff quarters, outdoor terrace, teppanyaki station, and outdoor seating areas. The larger residences also feature a private study, cinema room, and sunken seating.
Completion Date: The project is currently under construction, with the anticipated completion date set for Q4 2024.

One Canal offers an unparalleled luxury lifestyle in Dubai, making it an ideal choice for families and young couples seeking spacious, high-end living spaces in a prime location.

Bulgari Lighthouse stands as a beacon of opulence and architectural excellence on the private peninsula of Jumeirah Bay Island in Dubai, UAE. Developed by Meraas Holding and meticulously crafted by the renowned architectural firm Antonio Citterio Patricia Viel, this 28-storey residential tower is poised to redefine luxury living in the city. With an expected completion date in 2025, Bulgari Lighthouse offers a limited collection of 31 exclusive apartments, each showcasing the highest standards of craftsmanship and elegance. Below, we delve into the finer details of this exceptional residential masterpiece.
Architectural Brilliance
Bulgari Lighthouse's distinctive architectural design draws inspiration from a lighthouse, embodying its iconic tapering shape and vertical lines. The tower is clad in black and gold Paonazzo marble, which not only adds to its visual grandeur but also creates a mesmerizing shimmering effect when kissed by the sunlight. This exterior design symbolizes luxury and exclusivity from the very first glance.
Luxurious Interiors
Upon stepping inside Bulgari Lighthouse, residents are enveloped in luxury. The apartments are generously spacious, boasting high ceilings, marble floors, and meticulously curated custom-made furniture. The lavish interiors seamlessly blend elegance and functionality, setting a new standard for residential comfort.
Gaggenau-Equipped Kitchens
For culinary enthusiasts, Bulgari Lighthouse offers state-of-the-art kitchens equipped with Gaggenau appliances. These gourmet spaces are not only practical but also an aesthetic delight, ensuring every meal preparation is a culinary masterpiece.
Marble-Finished Bathrooms
The opulence extends into the bathrooms, adorned with exquisite marble finishes. But what truly sets them apart are the bathtubs with captivating views, offering a serene escape within the confines of your home.
World-Class Amenities
Bulgari Lighthouse leaves no stone unturned when it comes to providing residents with an exceptional lifestyle. The tower's amenities are second to none and include a private beach, a splendid swimming pool, a rejuvenating spa, a fully-equipped gym, and a rooftop terrace that grants breathtaking panoramic vistas of the city.
Residents' Club
For those seeking more refined leisure, Bulgari Lighthouse features a residents' club that encompasses a library, a games room, and a private cinema. It's the perfect setting for socializing, relaxing, and indulging in leisurely pursuits.
Bulgari Branded Living
Exclusive Prestige
Bulgari Lighthouse enjoys the distinction of being the sole residential tower on Jumeirah Bay Island branded by Bulgari, one of the world's most esteemed luxury brands. This association elevates the development's prestige, ensuring residents experience luxury at its finest.
Project Details
Exclusive Unit Selection
Bulgari Lighthouse offers a limited selection of 31 units, comprising 24 four-bedroom apartments and 7 five-bedroom apartments. The units vary in size, ranging from 3,000 to 6,000 square feet, providing options to suit diverse lifestyles and preferences.
Dedicated Amenity Floor
An entire floor is dedicated to amenities, offering unparalleled luxury and convenience. This floor includes a private beach, an enticing swimming pool, a world-class spa, a fitness center, a residents' club, and a rooftop terrace that serves as a serene retreat.
Harmony of Architecture and Nature
Bulgari Lighthouse's architecture is deeply rooted in its natural surroundings. The building's design draws inspiration from coral, symbolizing protection, privacy, and tranquility. Layers of architectural coral create stylish, livable outdoor spaces on every floor, connecting residents to the natural world around them.
Illuminating the Skyline
True to its name, Bulgari Lighthouse rises majestically from sea to sky, casting a captivating glow on the skyline. Light is fundamental to the design, with the faade's lighting taking inspiration from the gentle movements of marine corals, creating living and breathing light patterns that evolve from day to night.
Impeccable Service and Surroundings
Adjacent Bulgari Resort Services
Residents of Bulgari Lighthouse enjoy a seamless blend of privacy and attentive service. The adjacent Bulgari Resort manages and services every aspect of the property, ensuring residents' needs are met with precision. 
Mediterranean Gardens and Pools
The immaculate Mediterranean gardens enveloping the residences provide exclusive and private spaces for residents to unwind. These gardens flow gracefully around the building and converge at a luxurious deck suspended over the sea. From the Beach Edge Pool to the 50-meter long Horizon Pool, Bulgari Lighthouse offers a variety of tranquil spaces to relax, complete with private cabanas for ultimate comfort.
Penthouse Living
Four and Five-Bedroom Penthouses
For those seeking the pinnacle of luxury, Bulgari Lighthouse offers four and five-bedroom penthouses. These penthouses are accessible by private elevators and feature dramatic double-height living spaces that open onto expansive balconies with private pools. A master bedroom suite, four king rooms, family spaces, and extensive service areas ensure that residents experience unparalleled grandeur and comfort.

MESMERISING VIEWSSoak in the different sides of Dubai with stunning panoramic views. From the shimmering lights of Bluewaters reflecting off the water to the bright lights of JBR adorning the sky, to the open expanse of the Gulf - there's a view for every outlook.
THE AIN DUBAIMarvel at the worlds tallest and largest observation wheel. Inspiring, iconic and standing at 250m tall, its a breathtaking piece of engineering that will leave you in awe. One of many unforgettable perspectives of Dubai, best enjoyed from the comfort of your own home.
SEAVIEWSSoak in the gentle movements of water as they create living and breathing light patterns that evoke a sense of solace. Enjoy the rising sun spill over the horizon at dawn and watch yachts dot the coastline by day. And at dusk indulge in unforgettable shades of light as the dimming sun nestles into the waters of the Gulf.
CITYSCAPESDay or night, the citys skyline will take your breath away. Breathe in  the splendor of the architecture the city has to offer. Watch the morning fog gently envelop all the buildings and the twinkling of the night lights as you gaze at the cityscape.
AMENITIESA community that boasts a wide range of amenities, exclusive to all our residents, that reinvigorate both body and mind. From world-class exercise and meditation facilities, to pools with a view, to secure family spaces, indulge in facilities deserving of the Bluewaters brand.
CONTEMPORARY STYLINGWhere land meets sea. Bluewaters Bay is a place where open-plan apartment layouts and contemporary styling offer a true sense of grandeur. At the heart of Bluewaters Bay lies a philosophy that has inspired furnishing and spaces - all styled and designed to evoke calm, sanctuary and comfort.
MODERN DESIGNHomes that are defined by subtle elegance and a sophisticated finish. With Miami living as our architect's muse, floor to ceiling glass allows light to flood into living spaces. All facets of this development have been designed to provide everything you could possibly need for a truly exceptional living experience.
URBAN HAVENLuxuriate in vast open spaces that let you discover your best self. Discover pathways that lead to serene nature and glitzy cityscapes.
BEACHFRONT LIVINGTake solace in soft, inviting white sands as you stroll on idyllic beaches. Dip your toes in the tranquility of the ocean as you find a new sense of calm. Watch the sea glisten as you dive into the aquamarine sea. Experience life by the beach like no other.
LUXURIOUS LIFESTYLEWalk along a vibrant tapestry of busy boulevards filled with bustling restaurants where you can indulge in your favorite dishes. Turn the corner and find tranquil spaces where you can soak in natural landscapes enveloped by the vastness of the Arabian Sea.
LIVING SPACESDesigned to let the inside-out and the outside-in, all of our interior living spaces have been inspired by a lifestyle thats in perfect harmony with the surrounding world. Quite simply, these are spaces for mind and body best enjoyed with family and friends.
SOPHISTICATED DECORWake up to rooms filled with early morning light, elegantly and tastefully curated. Dcor at Bluewaters Bay has been carefully deliberated upon and designed to bring the outside in. From open-plan, modern kitchens, to bedrooms with dreamy views. Here, you can experience open living in apartments that invite tranquility and vibrancy inside.

Infinity pool
Sports facilities, including a zone for yoga, aerobics, a skate park, and a health club
Sauna and steam rooms
Valet and concierge services
Pet-friendly zone
Retail and dining options

Sobha Seahaven is conveniently located near Sheikh Zayed Road, providing easy access to other areas of Dubai, as well as to key attractions and landmarks, such as Downtown Dubai, Dubai Marina, and Palm Jumeirah.

Purchasing a residential unit with a cost from AED 2,000,000 provides you and your family with an opportunity to apply for a ten year Golden UAE Visa after the handover date. The visa can be prolonged if you remain the owner of the property.

Sobha Seahaven is a unique development that offers a number of advantages over other waterfront developments in Dubai. Here are just a few reasons why you should choose Sobha Seahaven:

Prime location: Sobha Seahaven is located in the Mouth of Dubai Harbour, which is one of the most desirable locations in Dubai. It is close to all of the major attractions and landmarks, as well as to Sheikh Zayed Road, which provides easy access to other areas of the city.
Luxurious apartments: The apartments at Sobha Seahaven are designed to the highest standards and feature premium finishes and appliances. Smart home system and state-of-the-art home appliances will also be featured in Sobha Seahaven.
World-class amenities: Sobha Seahaven offers a wide range of world-class amenities, including an infinity pool, sports facilities, sauna and steam rooms, valet and concierge services, and a pet-friendly zone.
Golden Visa eligibility: Purchasing a residential unit at Sobha Seahaven makes you eligible to apply for a ten year Golden UAE Visa.

If you are looking for a luxurious waterfront development in Dubai with a convenient location and a wide range of amenities, then Sobha Seahaven is the perfect choice for you.

Experience the epitome of luxury living at Como Residences, a prestigious residential development strategically located on the renowned Palm Jumeirah in Dubai. Nestled in the heart of this iconic man-made archipelago, Como Residences offers residents unrivaled access to Dubai's major attractions and leisure destinations. A short drive takes you to Aquaventure Waterpark, The Lost Chambers Aquarium, Nakheel Mall, and more. Additionally, the vibrant Dubai Marina is within easy reach, providing a diverse range of entertainment and dining options.
Architectural Marvel: A Seashell-Inspired Oasis
Rising majestically to 71 stories, Como Residences is a true architectural masterpiece. Its design pays homage to the gentle curves of an organic seashell, harmonizing seamlessly with the natural beauty of Palm Jumeirah. The exterior of the tower is a captivating testament to the sea and sand, creating an iconic landmark on the island.
Luxurious Interiors: Uncompromising Elegance
Step inside Como Residences and immerse yourself in opulent, contemporary interiors. Every inch is thoughtfully designed, boasting high-quality finishes and fixtures that elevate the living experience to unparalleled levels of luxury. The attention to detail is apparent in every corner, promising a life of sophistication and comfort.
Diverse Unit Types: Tailored to Your Lifestyle
Como Residences caters to a variety of lifestyles with its diverse range of unit types. Choose from 2-bedroom apartments to 7-bedroom duplexes, or ascend to the pinnacle of luxury in the exclusive penthouse. Each unit features spacious balconies or terraces that offer sweeping views of the Arabian Gulf, adding to the allure of waterfront living.
Amenities Beyond Compare: A World of Luxury Awaits

Private Sandy Beach: Indulge in the luxury of your own private sandy beach, a rare gem in the heart of the city.
Rooftop Infinity Pool: Dive into the rooftop infinity pool and immerse yourself in breathtaking panoramic vistas.
25-Meter Lap Pool: For those who love swimming, a 25-meter lap pool awaits your enjoyment.
Fully Equipped Gym: Maintain your fitness routine in a state-of-the-art gym with top-notch equipment.
Spa and Salon: Relax and rejuvenate at the on-site spa and salon, offering a range of wellness treatments.
Business Center: Conduct business seamlessly with the convenience of a dedicated business center.
Children's Play Area: Keep the little ones entertained in a safe and well-designed play area.
Residents' Lounge: Socialize and unwind in the exclusive residents' lounge, fostering a sense of community.

Exclusive Features: Elevating Luxury to New Heights
Como Residences offers unique features that set it apart:

Sculpted Vertical Lakes: The tower features vertical lakes housing communal pools and premium private pools, complementing the sky terrace residences.
Concierge Services: Enjoy full concierge services, ensuring your needs are met with the highest level of care and attention.
Abundant Parking: Each residence includes 36 parking spaces, while penthouse owners are treated to a generous allocation of 10 parking spaces.

Proximity to Attractions: Living the Dream
Como Residences offers the privilege of being close to iconic entertainment venues on Palm Jumeirah:

Aquaventure Waterpark: Experience over 105 record-breaking slides and thrilling attractions.
The Lost Chambers Aquarium: Immerse yourself in a mesmerizing underwater world with over 65,000 creatures.
Nakheel Mall: A retail and dining paradise with over 140 stores and 30 dining venues.
Dubai Marina: Just a 10-minute drive away, offering Dubai Marina Mall and a vibrant atmosphere.

Ease of Access: Proximity to Business and Travel

Business districts like Business Bay and Downtown Dubai are within a 20-minute drive, ideal for professionals.
Dubai International Airport is conveniently located just a 25-minute car ride from the development.

Scheduled Completion: A Vision Becoming Reality
The prestigious Como Residences project is set to be handed over in Q3 2027, promising residents a life of luxury, security, and comfort in one of Dubai's most sought-after locations.
Como Residences on Palm Jumeirah isn't just a place to live; it's an embodiment of extravagance, elegance, and exclusivity. From its sea-inspired architecture to its world-class amenities, Como Residences sets a new standard for luxury living in Dubai. This is your opportunity to call one of Dubai's most prestigious locations home, where every day is a testament to opulence and comfort.

DAMAC Cavalli Couture is an exclusive and luxurious residential project brought to life by DAMAC Properties, in collaboration with the legendary fashion house of Roberto Cavalli. Nestled along the picturesque banks of the Dubai Water Canal, this project redefines opulent living in one of the most desirable areas of Dubai. With a limited number of super-luxury residences, Cavalli Couture sets a new standard for upscale living, offering residents a harmonious lifestyle with access to key landmarks and a myriad of attractions.
Property Types
Cavalli Couture presents a selection of meticulously designed apartments, including 3, 4, and 5-bedroom units, showcasing high-end design at every turn. The 3-4 bedroom apartments feature floor areas starting at 4,300 sqft, while more spacious 5-bedroom duplexes boast living areas from 8,750 sqft. Each of the 70 super-luxury residences in this 12-story building enjoys unobstructed views of the Dubai Water Canal.
Location
This project is strategically situated on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal, offering breathtaking waterfront views. It also resides within the 64-hectare Safa Park, celebrated for its lush natural surroundings and top-notch entertainment and recreational amenities. The location provides easy access to key landmarks in Dubai.
Amenities
Residents of Cavalli Couture are treated to an array of top-notch amenities that enhance their vibrant and tranquil lifestyle. On the rooftop, a swimming pool and a lounge zone await, where residents can savor exclusive dishes prepared by a chef. The project promises waterfront views of the canal, adding to its allure.
Shopping and Entertainment
The vicinity of Cavalli Couture offers an abundance of shopping and entertainment options. The Dubai Mall, one of the world's largest shopping centers, is nearby, featuring 1,200 retail stores, 200 dining options, and various entertainment activities. City Walk, an outdoor retail complex, provides a plethora of fashion brand stores, restaurants, and entertainment venues, including Roxy Cinemas and The Green Planet, an indoor tropical forest.
Recreation
For sports enthusiasts and nature lovers, the Meydan Academy & Driving Range is just a 15-minute drive away. The Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary, known for its diverse bird population, offers a unique experience. Additionally, the development is conveniently located near Jumeirah Beach and Sunrise Beach for those seeking seaside leisure.
Pricing and Payment Plan
The starting price for these luxury residences is AED 16,500,000. A flexible payment plan of 70-30 is available, with an initial 70% payment and the remaining 30% to be settled later.
Why Choose DAMAC Cavalli Couture?

Central Park Plaza, located within the highly sought-after development of City Walk in Dubai, is a prestigious project by Meraas. This final phase of the Central Park community offers an exceptional opportunity for residents and investors alike. Here's a detailed project overview:
Central Park Plaza: The Ultimate Living Experience
Central Park Plaza represents the final chapter in the Central Park community, making it the last chance to invest in this prestigious development. Meraas offers various residences within Central Park Plaza, featuring different layouts with stunning views of the community and the Dubai skyline.
Residents will enjoy harmonious living just minutes away from key areas of the emirate, creating a perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility.
Luxurious Onsite Amenities
Central Park Plaza provides access to all the exciting amenities available within Central Park itself. These include a basketball half-court, a children's nursery, a dog park, an events area, games tables, and more.
Prime Location in Dubai
Central Park Plaza enjoys a strategic location within easy reach of some of Dubai's most popular attractions, including the Coca-Cola Arena, Museum of the Future, and The Green Planet.
Thanks to its proximity to Sheikh Zayed Road, residents will have easy access to navigate around Dubai. Multiple public transport links, including Rostamani Tower, Emirates Tower Metro Station, and Financial Center Station, further enhance convenience.
Abundant Sports and Leisure Amenities
Residents have access to a plethora of sports, leisure, and entertainment amenities throughout Central Park in City Walk, including an infinity pool, children's pool, green areas, picnic pavilions, outdoor BBQ areas, a children's playground, yoga and meditation areas, multi-use sports lawns, tennis and squash courts, a half-basketball court, a mini golf course, and a dog park.
Convenience and Accessibility
Central Park Plaza offers a convenient lifestyle with City Walk's retail, dining, and entertainment venues just a short walk away.
Downtown Dubai and Business Bay are both less than 10 minutes away by car, ensuring swift travel to major business and leisure hubs.
Investment Potential


Profitable Investment: Investors have the opportunity to realize a 1520% profit upon completion of the project, making Central Park Plaza an attractive choice for those looking to grow their wealth through real estate.


Rental Income: Alternatively, property owners can choose to rent out their units for short- or long-term periods, with an average rental yield of 8.8% for 1-bedroom apartments in the vicinity.


Why Choose Central Park Plaza?
Central Park Plaza is an exclusive real estate development offering an unparalleled living experience with world-class amenities, prime location, and promising investment opportunities in the heart of Dubai's vibrant City Walk. Don't miss your chance to be a part of this exceptional community.

Nestled on the prestigious Palm Jumeirah, One Crescent stands as an exclusive ultra-luxury residential development that redefines craftsmanship and sophistication. Developed by AHS Properties, a part of the esteemed AHS Group, this iconic complex is a testament to opulent living.
One Crescent boasts an awe-inspiring wave-like integrated architecture, featuring individual residential swimming pools and green pockets gracing every curve of its stunning facade. The project showcases the exceptional design talents of the award-winning tech-driven architect and designer, Shaun Killa, renowned for his work on iconic structures like the Museum of the Future, the Dubai Opera, and the Burj Khalifa.
Property Features

Limited Exclusive Properties: One Crescent offers only 25 super-refined properties, providing residents with a sense of exclusivity and luxury.
Breathtaking Views: Residents will enjoy stunning panoramic views of the ocean, the iconic Burj Al Arab, and the renowned Dubai skyline.
Luxurious Residences: One Crescent features gorgeous 3 to 4-bedroom penthouses, 5-bedroom Sky Villas, and spacious 6-bedroom Sky Mansions, offering a range of options to suit various lifestyles.
Spacious Living: The available real estate for purchase ranges from 3,800 sq. ft to an expansive 16,300 sq. ft, providing ample space for comfortable living.
Private Amenities: Each residence comes with a private outdoor terrace, a swimming pool, and a spacious entertainment area, offering a premium living experience.

Pricing

Penthouse: The starting price for a magnificent penthouse at One Crescent is AED 15,000,000 (USD 4,084,000), reflecting the exclusivity and luxury of the development.
Sky Villa: A glamorous Sky Villa can be acquired for a minimum of AED 32,500,000 (USD 8,849,000), providing residents with the epitome of opulent living.
Sky Mansion: The fantastic Sky Mansion is available for a minimum of AED 55,000,000 (USD 14,975,000), offering an unmatched level of luxury and grandeur.

One Crescent sets a new standard for premium living in Dubai, combining exceptional design, breathtaking views, and a limited number of exclusive residences. This ultra-luxury development promises an unparalleled living experience on Palm Jumeirah.

Mercedes-Benz Places is a collaborative venture between Binghatti Developers and luxury automotive giant Mercedes-Benz, located in the heart of Downtown Dubai. This iconic residential project features 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments as well as penthouses, soaring to an impressive height of 341 meters across 65 floors, redefining opulence in the city's skyline.
Strategically positioned, the development offers unobstructed views of the renowned Burj Khalifa, surrounded by iconic structures such as the Dubai Mall and the Museum of the Future. The partnership between the developer and Mercedes-Benz is dedicated to a customer-centric approach, prioritizing the needs and desires of future residents.
Architectural excellence is a key highlight, boasting floor-to-ceiling heights of 4.2 meters that provide a sense of spaciousness and luxury. Each unit is adorned with a private pool, offering residents an exclusive retreat within their homes. The panoramic views from every unit facing the Burj Khalifa create an awe-inspiring living environment, incorporating the automotive giant's design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity' to create timeless and beautiful spaces.
The project, a result of meticulous planning and design, incorporates smart home technologies and intelligent mobility solutions, aiming to redefine comfort and convenience in modern living spaces. It envisions a lifestyle that seamlessly combines sophistication with the exclusivity of an oasis.
Key highlights include a premium collection of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments and penthouses, an astounding elevation of 341 meters across 65 floors, strategic location in Downtown Dubai, private pools in each residence, and adherence to the Mercedes-Benz design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity.'
In summary, Mercedes-Benz Places is an exclusive residential complex embodying ultra-luxury services, a collaboration between renowned developers and the iconic Mercedes-Benz brand, offering a harmonious oasis of serenity, aesthetic appeal, and a lifestyle that seamlessly blends automotive excellence with architectural grandeur.
